Description:
Country Home With Huge Garage
Situated in a private, quiet hills location is this unique home on a large totally usable allotment of 1/3 of an acre. The home offers 2 large bedrooms, large main bathroom with spa bath, spacious open plan living areas consisting of kitchen/meals area and an adjoining comfortable lounge room with coonara heating, Gas ducted heating and split system, there is also space for an open study nook.
The cottage style gardens are low maintenance with a great rear under cover patio area ideal for entertaining and a HUGE 4 car garage with remote door and an separate internal room and wood/storage shed around behind the shed, outside you will also find a separate paddock, containing vegie garden, chook run, small stables and storage shed. This unique property promises a cosy, family haven while being close to all amenities. Call today this one won't last!!

Description:
AFFORDABLE 3 BEDROOM HOME. CLOSE TO EVERYTHING!
This tidy 3 BDR Western Red Cedar Home sits privately at the back of a nicely treed acre block only 600 metres from the main street of Cockatoo, the primary school, shops & public transport. Featuring an elevated view from the front verandah, enter into the large lounge room with floor to ceiling windows, which let in heaps of natural light, & a reverse cycle split system to keep you warm in winter & cool in summer at the touch of a button. The 3 BDRs are all spacious, 1 offering a double built in robe & the light filled Master with a large bay window & walk in robe. The open plan kitchen meals area offers gas cooking & is the central hub of the home separating the Master Bedroom from the others. In the spacious bathroom there is a large corner shower & a corner spa to relax away the aches of the day. Add to this mains gas, water & electricity, made road access, a small, low maintenance, fenced rear yard with garden shed & large bushy front yard to protect your privacy all less than a minute from Cockatoo. First home or investment you will not be disappointed!
CALL TO ARRANGE A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY!

The Ultimate Hills Escape On 3/4 Of An Acre (approx)

The heart of the home is the large country style kitchen that offers gas cooking, dishwasher; plenty of cupboards space & room to move. There are three bedrooms master bedroom is roomy with a large walk-in robe & direct access to the front verandah. To enjoy this rare and unique home on this magnificent property with bush surroundings call today!

The Mud Brick Sanctuary

The home offers 3 spacious bedrooms, master offering enough room for a home office or parents retreat & a beautifully designed family bathroom mixing the elegance of the old with the convenience of the new. Other features of the home include split system heating and cooling unit in the main living areas, ducted vacuum,
vaulted ceilings throughout, 3 TV's and new carpets throughout! Outside you will discover manicured gardens, large lawn areas, garden shed, 2x 5000L water tank, single carport and every path through the garden leads to a peaceful and private sanctuary where you can sit back and relax or even entertain with friends.
Conveniently located just a short distance from the Cockatoo Primary School, public transport, the local shops & a variety of eateries the home has all the charm & convenience you could wish for!

A BEAUTIFULLY FINISHED COTTAGE ON AROUND 1/4 OF AN ACRE
With its private lane entry, verandah, garden surrounds and a split level cottage in perfect condition, this property on around 1/4 of an acre offers instant comfort and appeal for a wide range of buyers. From the broad parking area at the end of the lane you step down through the ferns and flowers to the classic weatherboard styled cottage with a full width verandah that doubles as an entry and relaxing outdoor retreat. Inside, polished hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings and timber highlights combine to create a welcoming interior where the lounge and dining rooms sit on separate levels with gas and Coonara style wood heaters offering winter respite. The newly renovated kitchen offers flexibility with its movable island bench and the custom finished pressed metal splashbacks hark back to its classic roots. There are 3 robed bedrooms as well as a family bathroom with an adjoining toilet and laundry while outside you find generous under house storage, plenty of tall trees and a flat grassed area for kids or entertaining. Just a few minutes from central Cockatoo, the home is within easy reach of Cockatoo Primary School, buses and local shops.

Description:
STYLISH FAMILY HOME WITH 6 BEDROOMS ON HALF AN ACRE!
This stylishly renovated family home just minutes from Cockatoo & a 15 minute drive to Pakenham & the Freeway offers 6 extremely spacious bedrooms, 3 living areas, 3 bathrooms & 4 toilets, all on a landscaped half acre with an enormous deck for outdoor entertaining. The home features 2 large bedrooms with built in robes, (one with a separate study nook) & a bathroom at one end of the home off the huge rumpus room with access to the outdoor entertaining area. The well-appointed, contemporary kitchen features a 900mm free standing gas stove with electric oven, heaps of bench space, plenty of cupboards & a spacious pantry, whilst the adjacent laundry offers external undercover access, a 4th toilet & plenty of room to store all those muddy boots during winter. The kitchen overlooks another living area with a formal dining area & has access to a 2nd traditionally styled bathroom with corner spa & a generous linen cupboard. Down the hall is the Master Bedroom with built in robes & ensuite & 3 further extra sized bedrooms, one of which could easily be converted to a rumpus or theatre room. The home features mains GDH, a split system in the family room, polished floors, floating floors, quality carpets, ducted vacuum & full length windows throughout, letting in an abundance of natural light. Outside the rear yard is fully fenced, perfect for your furry family & there is a lock up garage/workshop & a convenient circular drive with an ornamental treed canopy to provide a natural shelter for your cars. Add to this the convenience of mains gas, water & sewer & there is nothing left to do but move in & enjoy. Inspection is sure to impress!
CALL TO ARRANGE A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY!

Description:
DOUBLE THE SIZE AND TWICE AS NICE...
With everything a growing family could possibly want, this home is large enough to accommodate everyone! You will be impressed with the stunning timber kitchen with stainless steel appliances that overlooks a relaxed meals area and also a large lounge and rumpus room that is the perfect place for all to enjoy. Another spacious lounge room provides access to the wide timber decking and is a great space for kids to have their own little bit of privacy. Four bedrooms plus an ideal downstairs home office / games room adds to the generous size of this home and allows the whole family to grow and expand over many years and still have enough room to move. The property has direct access from the rear to the Cockatoo / Mountain Road reserve where you can take the bikes or a footy and enjoy many acres of greenery all within a quick walk from your own back door. With a sealed drive and double carport, this home will be double the size of anything else you have seen and certainly twice as nice....

Description:
AFFORDABLE 9 ACRE+ EQUESTRIAN PROPERTY!
This comfortable 3 bedroom family home is situated on over 9 acres walking distance to the Primary School, public transport & Cockatoo central. Featuring a menage, 2 outdoor stables, a horse wash, 2 horse boxes, a huge shed/workshop with internal stable & over 9 acres of paddock, this is the ideal horse lover's property! The light filled home takes in the valley views from every window & features 3 spacious bedrooms, 1 with a walk in robe & ensuite, the 2nd with ensuite effect to the main bathroom & a third huge bedroom upstairs that could be easily converted to a Master Suite. The well-appointed central kitchen offers electric cooking, dishwasher & sensational views over the menage & the valley. Adjacent to the kitchen is a large lounge area with toasty wood heater & a spacious dining area with split system for added comfort & convenience. The living area opens onto a sensational deck, featuring a large undercover entertaining area with cafe blinds to make it a comfortable place to entertain all year round, as well an enclosed yard, ideal for the little ones & a spa where you can relax with friends & still keep an eye on the young rider in the arena or just enjoy the peaceful outlook. With dual entry from Amphlett Avenue, multiple paddocks, mains water, a huge double carport ideal for the float & double entry drive, this home offers an affordable paradise to the horse & animal lover!
CALL TO ARRANGE A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY!

Description:
CAPTIVATING MUD BRICK COTTAGE!
Conveniently located just a few hundred metres from the Cockatoo Primary School, public transport, the local shops & a variety of eateries this 3 (potentially) 4 bedroom mud brick cottage will take your breath away with its rustic charm & character. As you enter the open plan living area you will immediately feel the warmth of the home with soaring cathedral ceilings, polished floors & white painted mud brick walls. The well-appointed timber kitchen with 900mm free standing gas stove with double electric oven is perfect for the budding chef, whilst the kitchen overlooks the comfortable lounge with mains gas Coonara style heating, perfect for entertaining. Down the hall there are 3 spacious bedrooms & a beautifully designed bathroom mixing the elegance of the old with the convenience of the new featuring a claw foot bath, antique vanity & seamless shower. Upstairs, overlooking the lounge is a huge loft area ideal as a second living area/study or 4th bedroom - the choice is yours. Outside there is over a quarter of an acre of established, low maintenance gardens, 2 single carports, a sealed drive & magnificent verandahs to insulate the home from the weather & offer the perfect spot to entertain all year round. Add to this all mains services connected & this home has all the charm & convenience you could wish for!
CALL TO ARRANGE A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY!
